Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.39,0:00:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天开始的暑假  大家要有意义地度过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是高三的各位有夏季讲习  夏天…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  1  2  1  2…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去合宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是合宿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.28,0:00:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去  想去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  迎考复习…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成合宿的人～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.91,0:00:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事也要向梓征求一下意见…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.86,0:00:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发消息问过梓喵了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4对1啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:41.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今年也去合宿！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎大家到来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  大家都来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快进来  快进来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是懒散啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来玩游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.87,0:02:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要玩  要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:36.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯会玩格斗游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:38.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春子借给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是为什么聚到这里来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是为了商量合宿的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快点开始啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  稍微玩一下也没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.55,0:02:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…去合宿真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  为什么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:02:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐你们都已经是高三了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微松口气嘛  松口气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是「稍微」而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年和前年去了海边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今年去爬山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  今年也去海边好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在河里抓了鱼还能烧烤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然玩的兴致很浓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  梓想去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我想去参加山里的夏日节
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日减？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日肚脐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夏日节
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种乐队在宽敞的野外会场进行演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有几万人聚集在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前就想去一次夏日节了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去听职业乐队的演奏也能增加经验
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这样定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日节是在山里举行的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会场是在山里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山里…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会被吃掉吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但肯定不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但票要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还能弄到手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你们没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是特别服务哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  你真是神出鬼没啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能给我来杯麦茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次参加夏日节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次参加野外演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以这么悠闲的心态去的话会输的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输给什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输给夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炙热耀眼的太阳  令人闷绝的热气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有此时守候着猎物的夏虫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加夏日节的人  要和这一切战斗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:04:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪学姐很有干劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:12.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（临时区间公车站）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  还没人来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  只有小梓一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然按时来的就只有和梓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪学姐没睡好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整晚都在挑选要听哪个乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是想看的乐队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会场好像也有好几个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴士已经来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打电话给唯学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的话就说一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～我想看看你们什么时候才会注意到我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我从没想过唯学姐会先到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  还有一个人没来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上去了演唱会  然后一直喝到早上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没睡就直接过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:33.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么明知今天要出发还做那种事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:35.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己说了要鼓足干劲的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晕车了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很合得来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和是宿醉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是ROCK派啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:50.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（On the rock：对酒精浓度较高的酒的一种狂热饮法，\N常直接称为rock，在rocks glass等中只加入冰后饮用。）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思  我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐很不适合坐车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个乐队和这个乐队一定要看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间相同却在不同会场嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要两个身体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两选一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者每个听一半
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想瞬间移动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪学姐在说任性的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃炒面  炒面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要吃炒面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐也在说小规模任性的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好嘛  律
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从早到晚都能听到演奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情绪一直很高涨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然高涨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在吃冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多好吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有土特产卖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  路边餐馆里什么都有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵也来尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高原特浓牛奶软冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息时间快要结束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我还没买土特产呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里又不是目的地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  在这里吃不到炒面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐也微妙地脱线了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯…这样很危险…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能赶上开幕式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会场里也有好吃的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  能完全沉浸在音乐中的两天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  炒面  我们去吃炒面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之尽情地去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  鼓足干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱线成这样没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大声说话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…  好多…  人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有这么多人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  在开始之前就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有三亿人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就超过日本的总人口了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠闲模式到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和是最悠闲的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说  你不是因为宿醉而精疲力尽了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经把昨天的我给抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是会场的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.46,0:09:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这以后就是战场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太夸张了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才用票换的腕套是进入摇滚祭典的通行证
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄丢的话就不能再入场了  要小心保护好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  在进去之前先去野营区
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要确保今晚睡的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平坦的地方已经没位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了  就在斜坡上忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  这样睡觉的时候不会脑充血吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头朝上不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很熟练啊  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  把行李都放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呵～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点闷热  但感觉很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是背后好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必需品都拿着了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防晒霜涂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝的东西买了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中暑对策很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去买运动饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个不要了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也带着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以洗手  或在热的时候往身上浇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水一定会帮上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样喜欢指挥的人还真存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不是运动鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没带别的鞋来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  把我的沙滩拖鞋借给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为能在河边玩就带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  驱虫剂涂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:11:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在来喷驱虫剂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  小澪也来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人想起小学时的郊游了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来我来帮喷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己能喷  没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我也想喷喷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…真像小学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会帮小律和梓喵喷的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要喷到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  要进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请为零垃圾运动出份力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里配发垃圾袋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了  夏日节
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我来进行会场内的说明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp150}　{\fsp1}Fire Stage{\r}\N首先是主打的烈火舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是能收纳约4万人的主会场之一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,场地呈平缓斜坡  所以后面也很容易观看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp250}　{\fsp1}Thunder Stage{\r}\N这里是被称为里主场的雷霆舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以收纳1万人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并有很多专业方向的乐队来演出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会经常往返这两个舞台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  距离大概约700米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算10秒跑完100米  也要花将近70秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放松点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有年轻乐队多出没的室内舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最里面的是爵士乐队和奇怪乐队较多的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有木吉他音乐人较多出没的小舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是音乐盛典
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭  饭在哪儿有卖？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  我要吃炒面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得这两个人哪里脱线了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来  还真亏小佐和有票呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个节日我每年都有来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可为什么会有6张？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来预定一起来的朋友突然取消了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和被讨厌了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没那回事啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我们情何以堪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  实际来了才发现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又热  人又多…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  让我们燃起来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音好大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是夏日节
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日节！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  小澪的初次夏日节
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这支乐队感觉不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  主唱的声音够沧桑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  大家  准备移动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想多听一下这支乐队啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最想推荐的乐队在室内舞台啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点远  我们要冲过去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  老师你就一个人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:30.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那我可去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律  律  我也想去雷霆舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快！再不快点的话就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿再联系集合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  梓喵也想再听下这个乐队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:15:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我穿着沙滩拖鞋跑不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们阔别三年再次回到这夏日摇滚的舞台来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律  律
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个乐队的吉他手是左撇子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然左手感觉很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这话由我来说有点不太妥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到伙伴很高兴我也懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微消停点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐在认真地看着表演
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果受到感染后能更加更加认真练习的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  我有事想问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个贝司手的发型是怎么弄出来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是天然卷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连学姐也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人气…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我们一起来排
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:15:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！还剩10份完售！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点  不可以屈服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们去买小唯想吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:16.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（海员沙司批萨）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦  我要回去～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别撒娇啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作得好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小律发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14点烈火舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15点雷霆舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16点再回烈火舞台…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  爽歪啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank You！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨变小了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到下一个想看的乐队出演还蛮久的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子不饿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭没吃成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是吃了可丽饼和冰激凌嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那不是饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去买晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们占位子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  木板道的中间不是有条小河吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在那儿等你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就先铺在这儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跳～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有卖T恤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个左手弹吉他的乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上试试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊  我也有点想要了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小佐和发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说她买了章鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章鱼烧～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好清爽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以洗澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我浑身痛痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓今年也是一身黑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然擦了防晒霜  但没有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱不就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我回去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  这就睡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇头舞过头了  脖子疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:18:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是不是认为我上年纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.98,0:19:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在听远处传来的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的一整晚都在演奏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  请就坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐着不动不会被蚊子咬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带着两个防虫带呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里谈悄悄话？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:19:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在这里听音乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得像梦一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  很不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这么广阔的地方  一直演奏着音乐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天看到的乐队都很帅气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  声音的气势…或者说魄力真是十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  还是我们的演奏更棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对专业人士你那是哪门子自信？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这话前  先学会不弹错吉他吧我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…一针见血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  还是我们的演奏更棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整体感啦  怎么说好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.74,0:21:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  是气场！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什么叫气场吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「放学后茶会」是个很好的乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错！就算是专业人士我们也不会落后的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连梓也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次不是作为听众
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要作为演奏者参加夏日节
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.17,0:21:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…这么起劲？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能在这里演出可就太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.62,0:21:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后我们也能一直组乐队就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:21:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:21:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就这样  直到永远吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里吃炒面味道真好啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.27,0:23:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  确实确实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.08,0:23:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  夏日节的时候学姐也非常期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.22,0:23:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最后因为卖完了而没吃到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:23:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有别墅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能去芬兰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.49,0:24:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带你们去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.87,0:24:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.86,0:24:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现剩下的午饭～


